<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(كان حيا ١١٨٠ هـ)</span> <span class="c2">(١٧٦٦ م)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
